# Cisco SPArk APIs

Collection of Python Scripts to manage spark rooms and messages based on the ciscosparkapi library

### RoomListSpark.py

Simple script to lists Cisco Spark rooms to which the authenticated user belongs.

### MessageSpark.py

Simple script to post a message in a Spark Room from authenticated user or on behalf of a bot.

# Installation

The scripts are based on the ciscosparkapi Python library.
You can install it manually using the pip Python Packages manager
```
pip install ciscosparkapi
```
or run the requirements after cloning this repo
```
git clone https://github.com/maccioni/ciscospark.git
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

# Usage

Simply run the script usng the Python interpreter, i.e.:
```
(spark) Mac:ciscospark $ python RoomListSpark.py
Searching existing rooms for Cat9K (id:Y2lzY29zcGFyazovL3VzL1BFT1BMRS83MzVkNDc5Ni01NjVjLTRmZmEtODU3Ny0yNzlkZTA4YmYwMjA)

     Room Name:                                  Room ID:
================================================================================
FabriRoom: Y2lzY29zcGFyazovL3VzL1JPT00vMzQzODRhMTAtMWE4Yi0xMWU3LTlmNzAtMzE5ZjUxNDkyOWNm

The current Spark user is part of 1 Spark rooms
```

